data.description: Beautiful 5-year-old home with partially shaded backyard near the end of the street in an established neighborhood. New engineered hardwood flooring in the living area and kitchen/dining. Baths have new luxury vinyl flooring. Garden tub in primary bath. Split bedroom plan, open kitchen, gas fireplace, and stainless steel kitchen appliances. Fenced backyard. Smart thermostat, security system, all appliances, including washer/dryer remain.
